Title: An Act Changing the Name of a Portion of the Schetelig Avenue in the City of San Pablo to Maximino M. Magcase Street
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 253
An Act Changing the Name of a Portion of the Schetelig Avenue in the City of San Pablo to Maximino M. Magcase Street
Section 1. The name of a portion of the Schetelig Avenue, from corner Balagtas Boulevard to corner T. Azucena and Barleta Streets, in the City of San Pablo is hereby changed to Maximino M. Magcase Street.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: November 12, 1982
